'''Miroljub Kostić''' ({{lang-sr-cyr|Мирољуб Костић}}; born 5 June 1988) is a [[Serbia]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays for the [[Uzbekistan Super League]] club [[FC AGMK|AGMK]].

==Honours==
;Jagodina
* [[Serbian Cup]]: [[2012–13 Serbian Cup|2012–13]]<ref name="soccerway">{{Soccerway|miroljub-kosti/144916}}</ref>

